CLOUD FORMATION is AWS service for provisioning the resources
creatd resources in predictable(output) repeatable and automated way

JSON Struture
--------------
AWS template format version= template version
description = what json going to do
metadata = properties
parameters = values {keyname, dbname, dbuser, dbpassword, instance type, ssh location}
mappings = dependencies
conditions = conditions
outputs = what stack will create
resources = simple tamplate for s3 bucket
Resources:
  
  S3BLD3O:

    Type: 'AWS::S3::Bucket'

    Properties: {}
